WEBVTT

00:08.521 --> 00:10.880
Very clever, Prince Song.

00:11.281 --> 00:12.880
If anything happens to Mr. Wu,

00:13.080 --> 00:14.921
His Majesty might think that our family

00:15.441 --> 00:17.041
attempted to eliminate

00:17.041 --> 00:18.201
a political rival.

00:18.801 --> 00:19.760
As for today's matter,

00:20.280 --> 00:22.481
I, the Magistrate of Shengtian,
can testify

00:22.491 --> 00:24.280
that Song Mo trespassed
on private property,

00:24.801 --> 00:27.421
threatened a court official
with a sword, and obstructed a rescue.

00:28.041 --> 00:30.801
Even if this matter is brought
before His Majesty,

00:30.801 --> 00:32.161
the facts remain the same.

00:36.160 --> 00:37.281
What a lively scene.

00:39.200 --> 00:40.440
Judging by the atmosphere,

00:41.361 --> 00:44.041
are you planning to perform
a sword dance?

00:45.080 --> 00:46.281
Greetings, Madam Cui.

00:47.520 --> 00:49.321
I was just chatting with my mother.

00:49.760 --> 00:50.641
What's going on here?

00:50.851 --> 00:52.001
It's all because of Dou Zhao.

00:52.051 --> 00:54.281
She refused to let Mr. Wu
be taken for medical treatment

00:54.281 --> 00:55.731
and insisted on treating him herself.

00:59.921 --> 01:00.681
Prince Song,

01:02.321 --> 01:05.041
haste makes waste,
calmness brings resolution.

01:05.640 --> 01:07.760
Duke of Ding has always been
a loyal and upright man.

01:07.761 --> 01:09.881
By overstepping your authority
to search his residence

01:09.881 --> 01:11.341
just to silence a political opponent,

01:11.480 --> 01:14.760
you will only end up harming your uncle.

01:15.081 --> 01:16.941
Please weigh the consequences
of your actions

01:17.041 --> 01:18.640
and be careful in your judgment.

01:19.601 --> 01:20.360
Madam Cui,

01:21.081 --> 01:22.400
while today's events

01:22.801 --> 01:24.200
cannot be taken to court,

01:24.480 --> 01:26.920
I know what I've seen.

01:27.881 --> 01:29.801
We've disrupted your peace today.

01:30.280 --> 01:32.760
I sincerely apologize.

01:34.861 --> 01:35.601
Everyone, withdraw.

01:43.360 --> 01:45.721
Master Dai, you've come
all the way here.

01:45.961 --> 01:47.400
Sorry I did not welcome you properly.

01:48.601 --> 01:51.881
But if you could spare me
from further conflict,

01:52.721 --> 01:54.441
I would be most grateful.

01:54.760 --> 01:56.640
Since you put it that way, Madam Cui,

01:58.760 --> 02:02.280
I will not pursue today's matter
any further.

02:02.640 --> 02:03.400
Everyone, leave.

02:06.560 --> 02:07.681
It's working.

02:08.041 --> 02:08.681
He's waking up.

02:09.721 --> 02:10.281
Dezhen.

02:11.721 --> 02:12.561
The doctor is here.

02:12.841 --> 02:13.640
Doctor, quickly!

02:28.281 --> 02:30.841
Lung abscesses are most dangerous
when they rupture internally.

02:30.851 --> 02:33.701
Thankfully, this young lady released the
clotted blood with acupuncture.

02:33.760 --> 02:35.680
Otherwise, he could have
suffocated to death.

02:46.841 --> 02:48.760
Madam, the young master
is out of danger now.

02:48.960 --> 02:50.601
I'll go prepare a decoction

02:50.601 --> 02:51.480
for him immediately.

02:51.680 --> 02:52.640
Follow me.

03:03.041 --> 03:06.561
Thank you, Fourth Young Lady,
for saving my life.

03:07.041 --> 03:08.431
Mr. Wu, there's no need to thank me.

03:09.151 --> 03:10.541
The credit goes to the Dou family.

03:11.051 --> 03:13.231
We'll make sure to send tonics
to your residence later.

03:13.601 --> 03:14.841
Lung abscesses are dangerous.

03:14.861 --> 03:16.001
You mustn't take it lightly.

03:16.131 --> 03:17.881
Take good care of your health
in the future.

03:20.001 --> 03:20.601
Dezhen,

03:21.161 --> 03:22.360
it's true she saved you,

03:22.841 --> 03:25.321
but your illness today
may not have been accidental.

03:27.080 --> 03:29.841
Just ask the Fourth Young Lady.

03:31.441 --> 03:32.041
Yantang,

03:33.161 --> 03:34.200
what are you suggesting?

03:35.200 --> 03:38.200
I contracted lung abscess
while assisting with disaster relief.

03:38.520 --> 03:40.161
Not even my grandfather knew about it.

03:40.680 --> 03:43.480
As for the phoenix butterfly incident,
no one could have foreseen it.

03:44.601 --> 03:46.360
You must be upset, Fourth Young Lady.

03:47.001 --> 03:49.841
I apologize on his behalf.

03:57.480 --> 04:00.881
Fourth Young Lady, you broke
societal conventions today

04:01.200 --> 04:02.441
to save my life.

04:02.680 --> 04:04.640
There's no way I can repay you,

04:05.640 --> 04:06.121
except...

04:06.121 --> 04:06.800
Mr. Wu,

04:07.080 --> 04:08.080
no need for words now.

04:08.960 --> 04:10.080
Focus on recovering.

04:10.520 --> 04:11.960
We can't hide this from your father.

04:12.451 --> 04:13.881
I'll escort you back to the capital.

04:14.920 --> 04:15.760
Suxin, Sulan.

04:16.041 --> 04:17.361
Lu Zheng, Lu Ming, come with us.

04:17.571 --> 04:18.161
- Yes.
- Yes.

04:27.281 --> 04:28.601
Thankfully, nothing bad happened.

04:29.281 --> 04:31.000
Prince Song should feel relieved now.

04:31.920 --> 04:33.641
Once Mr. Wu recovers,

04:34.120 --> 04:36.041
there will be no more misunderstanding.

04:37.041 --> 04:39.281
Quickly, help Mr. Wu to the guest room
to be treated.

04:43.201 --> 04:45.920
The embroidery is quite unique.

04:46.401 --> 04:46.841
Tell me,

04:47.560 --> 04:48.401
what is this?

04:50.081 --> 04:50.800
A tiger talisman.

04:51.320 --> 04:52.320
Is that it?

04:53.131 --> 04:55.041
I disregarded propriety just now
to save a life.

04:55.771 --> 04:57.440
It can well prove
I have nothing to hide.

05:18.560 --> 05:19.440
You're lying.

05:23.440 --> 05:24.761
You owe me an explanation.

06:57.501 --> 07:00.981
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

07:00.981 --> 07:03.701
=Episode 7=

07:03.981 --> 07:04.961
(Cui's Residence)

07:04.961 --> 07:05.821
Careful on the steps.

07:07.120 --> 07:08.480
I'm glad Mr. Wu is all right.

07:10.041 --> 07:11.521
Mr. Wu just suffered from heatstroke.

07:11.771 --> 07:12.721
He's now out of danger.

07:14.751 --> 07:15.641
No need to see us off.

07:15.641 --> 07:16.880
I'll say goodbye here.

07:20.771 --> 07:22.320
Thankfully, it ended without incident.

07:22.841 --> 07:25.120
At least the Wei family didn't witness
the earlier scene.

07:25.561 --> 07:27.551
The Fourth Young Lady
really has a temperament...

07:36.721 --> 07:37.360
Sister,

07:37.841 --> 07:40.120
I know the Fourth Young Lady
has feelings for me,

07:41.120 --> 07:43.440
but she is so uncouth.

07:44.341 --> 07:47.120
From now on, stop using expensive paper
and inkstone for calligraphy.

07:47.120 --> 07:48.560
Sell all the gardens and estates.

07:48.761 --> 07:49.761
If you can do that,

07:49.920 --> 07:51.320
I'll cancel the marriage proposal.

07:53.591 --> 07:56.240
When it comes to your treasures,
you can't bear to part with them.

07:56.461 --> 07:58.401
Now you understand
how difficult it's been for me

07:58.401 --> 07:59.411
to support the household.

07:59.560 --> 08:00.761
You have no idea

08:00.880 --> 08:02.320
how generous her dowry is.

08:02.551 --> 08:04.320
Gold and silver are just
superficial things.

08:04.521 --> 08:06.641
What matters in marriage
is mutual affection.

08:06.880 --> 08:08.440
Right now, only she has feelings for me.

08:08.920 --> 08:10.081
How can that work?

08:11.401 --> 08:14.281
You marry a wife for the sake
of the household.

08:14.401 --> 08:15.721
If you want mutual affection,

08:16.161 --> 08:17.521
take a concubine.

08:24.461 --> 08:26.751
Don't even think about
the Dou family's Fifth Young Lady.

08:26.771 --> 08:28.331
Her maternal grandfather is Wang Xingyi,

08:28.371 --> 08:30.201
and you've seen how capable
Wang Yingxue is.

08:30.440 --> 08:31.041
And you?

08:31.641 --> 08:33.161
All you have is a fancy title,

08:33.161 --> 08:35.631
with neither scholarly achievements
nor an official position.

08:36.611 --> 08:38.600
Titles and positions are just
superficial things.

08:39.471 --> 08:41.621
It's better not to be a greedy,
fame-chasing official.

08:43.440 --> 08:44.281
Fine, fine.

08:44.560 --> 08:45.560
As you wish.

08:46.121 --> 08:48.560
I'll think of it as marrying
a pair of cotton ear plugs

08:49.041 --> 08:50.241
to stop your constant nagging.

08:53.200 --> 08:55.200
When I retrieved this item from Mr. Wu,

08:55.680 --> 08:57.720
it was filled with the scent
of silk tree flowers.

09:00.320 --> 09:01.241
Silk tree flowers?

09:02.080 --> 09:03.161
As far as I know,

09:03.560 --> 09:05.320
there are no silk tree flowers nearby,

09:05.881 --> 09:07.920
let alone silk tree flower pollen.

09:08.401 --> 09:09.080
Exactly.

09:09.521 --> 09:11.041
It took me a while to figure it out.

09:11.481 --> 09:12.840
You soaked the tiger talisman

09:12.840 --> 09:14.481
in silk tree flower essence beforehand,

09:14.541 --> 09:16.771
leaving only its fragrance
and no trace of its presence.

09:17.121 --> 09:18.241
At the Dragon Boat Festival,

09:18.481 --> 09:21.080
the tiger talisman contained camphor
to mask its scent.

09:21.680 --> 09:24.560
Within an hour, the fragrance would have
completely dissipated.

09:25.361 --> 09:27.161
Luckily, Song Mo is a military man

09:27.560 --> 09:29.361
who has no idea of
the harem's scheming ways.

09:29.551 --> 09:31.600
Otherwise, your household
would be in deep trouble.

09:32.241 --> 09:34.241
These are baseless speculations.

09:34.401 --> 09:35.641
I suggest you watch your words.

09:37.001 --> 09:40.401
Years ago, you framed me
with ephedra poisoning,

09:40.800 --> 09:43.401
and now you've manipulated Mr. Wu,

09:43.680 --> 09:45.761
even swapping his tiger talisman
with Wei Tingyu's.

09:46.401 --> 09:47.121
Let me tell you,

09:47.481 --> 09:48.521
it won't work.

09:49.001 --> 09:50.960
Your destiny is to marry Wei Tingyu.

09:50.960 --> 09:52.401
I won't marry Wei Tingyu.

09:52.401 --> 09:54.281
Marriage is a matter decided by parents.

09:54.600 --> 09:55.720
It's not up to you.

09:56.161 --> 09:57.920
Wu Shan is my father's student,

09:58.200 --> 10:00.881
and I specifically chose him
as a husband for Ming.

10:01.121 --> 10:02.440
Don't even think about taking him.

10:03.001 --> 10:04.641
Madam Wei came today

10:05.080 --> 10:07.560
specifically to discuss your marriage
to Wei Tingyu.

10:08.361 --> 10:10.521
If I don't marry you off
to the Wei family,

10:11.041 --> 10:14.080
I would feel guilty.

10:14.720 --> 10:16.241
You're truly calculating.

10:33.751 --> 10:34.651
Are you feeling better?

10:36.661 --> 10:38.161
The Fourth Young Lady saved my life.

10:38.720 --> 10:39.840
You shouldn't doubt her.

10:40.320 --> 10:42.720
Did I ever say I doubted her?

10:43.281 --> 10:44.320
If you don't doubt her,

10:44.421 --> 10:45.881
why did you make such a fuss earlier?

10:46.481 --> 10:48.281
Dou Shishu is ambitious and scheming.

10:48.560 --> 10:50.080
Dou Shiying has no interest in power,

10:50.281 --> 10:51.481
but he's easily swayed.

10:51.751 --> 10:54.161
Wang Yingxue, on the other hand,
hides malice behind a smile.

10:54.481 --> 10:56.080
Your illness was most likely her doing.

10:56.800 --> 10:57.871
But judging by her reaction,

10:58.401 --> 10:59.720
even she doesn't want

10:59.851 --> 11:00.961
such a controversial matter

11:00.961 --> 11:02.881
to happen between you
and the Fourth Young Lady.

11:02.960 --> 11:04.171
As for the Fourth Young Lady...

11:05.401 --> 11:06.401
What about her?

11:07.481 --> 11:10.361
It's clear that she doesn't align
with the rest of the Dou family.

11:10.840 --> 11:11.800
But somehow,

11:11.800 --> 11:13.320
she accidentally caused you harm.

11:14.121 --> 11:15.920
Her actions to save you were sincere,

11:16.281 --> 11:17.481
but for the sake of her family,

11:17.600 --> 11:19.161
she chose to cover up the truth.

11:19.840 --> 11:20.720
Are you suggesting

11:21.440 --> 11:23.401
that the Fourth Young Lady
has feelings for me?

11:27.001 --> 11:28.001
If that were true,

11:29.041 --> 11:30.121
I'd be a lucky man.

11:30.401 --> 11:31.481
What I'm saying is,

11:31.840 --> 11:33.680
the Dou family is full
of scheming minds,

11:34.121 --> 11:35.361
and someone as simple as you

11:35.361 --> 11:36.401
can't handle them.

11:38.800 --> 11:40.560
I'm well aware of the darker side

11:41.200 --> 11:42.320
inside these noble families.

11:43.800 --> 11:45.161
But I'm not like you.

11:45.800 --> 11:48.960
I think being on the battlefield
has made you paranoid.

11:51.391 --> 11:53.371
The Fourth Young Lady
is intelligent and capable,

11:53.840 --> 11:54.720
a perfect match.

11:55.440 --> 11:56.720
You need to get it

11:57.281 --> 11:58.241
into your thick skull.

12:00.080 --> 12:02.761
You speak as if you know
the Fourth Young Lady better than I do.

12:02.920 --> 12:05.200
Have you secretly investigated her?

12:06.281 --> 12:07.241
You could say that.

12:08.571 --> 12:11.001
When you pulled me away
and stopped me from speaking earlier,

12:11.041 --> 12:12.031
I haven't even started...

12:14.281 --> 12:15.141
Still coughing?

12:15.151 --> 12:17.371
You shouldn't talk so much
when you have lung abscesses.

12:17.381 --> 12:19.771
I think the Fourth Young Lady's
medical skills are lacking.

12:20.241 --> 12:22.200
I'll ask a court physician
to examine you.

12:25.781 --> 12:28.261
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

12:32.600 --> 12:33.600
Sleeves, 1.8 feet long.

12:38.091 --> 12:39.080
Shoulders, 1.5 feet wide.

12:41.091 --> 12:42.320
His shoulders have grown wider.

12:42.600 --> 12:43.680
The cape needs altering.

12:46.121 --> 12:47.321
Good thing you held him back.

12:47.560 --> 12:49.600
Otherwise, that silly boy Dezhen

12:49.600 --> 12:51.641
would have insisted on repaying her
with marriage.

12:52.761 --> 12:53.440
You may leave.

12:56.391 --> 12:57.960
The Dou family uses underhanded tactics.

12:58.411 --> 13:01.801
When it comes to marriage, Old Master Wu
would never allow Dezhen to make decisions.

13:01.801 --> 13:03.881
Better to offend a nobleman
than provoke a villain.

13:04.320 --> 13:06.521
The Dou family, especially Dou Shishu,

13:06.881 --> 13:07.840
is like a venomous snake

13:07.920 --> 13:09.041
waiting to strike.

13:10.131 --> 13:13.031
Fortunately, the Dou family is quite
separated from the Cui Clan's Manor,

13:13.041 --> 13:15.200
and Madam Wang is openly hostile
toward Dou Zhao.

13:15.681 --> 13:17.320
Dou Shishu is deceitful
and power-hungry,

13:17.651 --> 13:19.221
while Dou Zhao is clever and strategic.

13:20.161 --> 13:23.161
If the two of them band together,
we'd be in serious trouble.

13:25.080 --> 13:27.561
I've heard she grew up
without the protection of her parents,

13:27.561 --> 13:29.080
so her life must have been difficult.

13:30.041 --> 13:32.521
It's only natural that she's
sensitive, thoughtful,

13:32.761 --> 13:33.720
and cautious.

13:35.800 --> 13:36.481
Sir.

13:38.920 --> 13:39.521
Sir.

13:39.761 --> 13:41.041
General Yan has sent a message

13:41.061 --> 13:43.741
that the phoenix butterfly incident
has nothing to do with Dou Zhao.

13:45.080 --> 13:45.680
As I expected.

13:49.241 --> 13:50.661
Although traveling by water is slow,

13:51.511 --> 13:53.241
Brother should arrive
in the capital soon.

13:56.361 --> 13:57.001
Mother,

13:57.840 --> 14:00.161
your urinary condition
leaves you dizzy and nauseous.

14:00.600 --> 14:02.600
Let the servants handle the sewing.

14:03.080 --> 14:04.440
Are you saying my sewing is poor?

14:06.161 --> 14:06.840
Come here.

14:08.731 --> 14:10.960
It's been so many years
since I mended clothes for you.

14:11.041 --> 14:13.771
This time, I'll finish the summer
garments for you and your brother.

14:14.281 --> 14:16.200
They'll be perfect for your trip
back to Futing.

14:17.241 --> 14:18.560
Mother, Brother.

14:22.041 --> 14:24.031
Young Master Song Han
brought you medicine, Madam.

14:28.161 --> 14:31.560
Brother, you finally came home, yet you've
been so busy keeping Mother company

14:31.560 --> 14:33.031
that you haven't spent time with me.

14:35.200 --> 14:37.001
Mother said you love grilled venison.

14:37.241 --> 14:39.200
I'm planning to hunt a deer
for you tomorrow.

14:39.361 --> 14:39.960
Great!

14:40.200 --> 14:41.600
If you can bring me venison,

14:41.960 --> 14:43.281
I'll ask Father to let you

14:43.600 --> 14:44.920
accompany me to Futing next year

14:45.571 --> 14:46.440
and join the military.

14:48.680 --> 14:49.920
Do you promise?

14:53.161 --> 14:54.840
Then we can arrange the prayers.

14:55.320 --> 14:56.641
Our ancestors

14:57.161 --> 14:59.001
should be informed
of Dou Zhao's marriage.

15:02.641 --> 15:04.241
Father, Fifth Uncle.

15:06.521 --> 15:08.121
I don't want this marriage.

15:11.440 --> 15:12.080
Dou Zhao,

15:13.440 --> 15:14.761
the court is unstable right now.

15:15.241 --> 15:16.960
It's obvious from Song Mo's actions.

15:17.440 --> 15:19.641
I worry he may not be able
to protect you all.

15:20.041 --> 15:22.121
You may be strong-willed,
but you are just a girl.

15:22.471 --> 15:23.981
If something happens to the Dou family,

15:24.161 --> 15:27.041
at least you'd have a husband
to protect you.

15:27.161 --> 15:28.481
I don't need anyone to protect me.

15:29.641 --> 15:32.281
All these years,
I've worked and studied hard,

15:32.361 --> 15:33.941
building a career and amassing wealth,

15:34.440 --> 15:36.800
so I wouldn't have to rely on anyone.

15:37.281 --> 15:38.881
I can protect myself.

15:39.121 --> 15:40.361
Do you think a little money

15:40.481 --> 15:41.881
can guarantee lifelong security?

15:42.641 --> 15:43.840
I've told you before,

15:44.291 --> 15:45.840
if a woman delays marriage for too long,

15:46.121 --> 15:47.200
she'll develop

15:47.200 --> 15:48.401
rebellious ideas.

15:48.431 --> 15:49.741
If I had known this would happen,

15:49.751 --> 15:52.461
I would've sent you off
in abridal sedan chair when you came of age.

15:52.461 --> 15:53.121
Even if you had,

15:53.361 --> 15:55.080
I would still refuse
to marry Wei Tingyu.

15:55.451 --> 15:56.241
You insolent girl!

15:56.241 --> 15:56.560
You...

15:57.080 --> 15:59.041
You've already done
such disgraceful things,

15:59.041 --> 16:00.631
and I haven't even dealt with you yet.

16:00.641 --> 16:02.401
You have no shame,
but the Dou family does.

16:02.401 --> 16:03.461
Shishu, what are you doing?

16:03.800 --> 16:04.680
Let's talk this out!

16:04.680 --> 16:05.800
Why are you hitting her?

16:06.881 --> 16:07.481
Dou Zhao.

16:09.641 --> 16:10.560
After all these years,

16:11.641 --> 16:13.200
you haven't changed one bit.

16:15.440 --> 16:17.080
I am your daughter,

16:18.680 --> 16:20.731
so why does Fifth Uncle
get to decide my marriage?

16:20.741 --> 16:22.901
- You disgraceful child, get out of my way!
- Shishu.

16:22.920 --> 16:24.451
- Get out of my way.
- Don't hit her!

16:24.461 --> 16:25.291
- Shishu!
- Enough!

16:27.200 --> 16:27.840
Mother.

16:28.161 --> 16:28.680
Mother.

16:28.680 --> 16:29.281
Get up.

16:32.401 --> 16:33.200
Are you all right?

16:37.521 --> 16:40.720
This marriage will have a big impact
on Dou Zhao's long-term happiness.

16:41.241 --> 16:43.320
How can you decide it so casually,

16:44.001 --> 16:46.320
treating her like an object
to be pawned?

16:47.200 --> 16:48.641
And who is Wei Tingyu?

16:49.161 --> 16:51.720
A man known for frequenting brothels
and having countless maids.

16:52.161 --> 16:53.840
He's bound to squander
his family fortune.

16:55.121 --> 16:58.320
Whoever decided on this engagement
should cancel it.

16:58.560 --> 16:59.001
Mother,

16:59.440 --> 17:01.001
Shishu and I didn't mean it like that.

17:01.800 --> 17:02.641
And what if we did?

17:03.041 --> 17:03.600
Mother,

17:03.720 --> 17:05.400
I am now the head of the Dou family.

17:05.841 --> 17:07.621
A womon unmarried
should defer to her father.

17:07.631 --> 17:09.391
A married woman
should defer to her husband.

17:09.451 --> 17:11.281
A woman's duty is to bear children, to support

17:11.291 --> 17:12.651
her husband
and raise children.

17:12.651 --> 17:15.160
The teachings state that
a father is a guide to his children.

17:15.191 --> 17:17.681
If the father is unkind, the child
may seek refuge elsewhere.

17:17.691 --> 17:18.971
A husband is a guide to his wife.

17:19.201 --> 17:21.160
If the husband is unworthy,
the wife may remarry.

17:21.521 --> 17:22.721
When did it ever say

17:22.961 --> 17:24.800
that women should be forced
into submission?

17:25.201 --> 17:25.560
You...

17:26.360 --> 17:28.281
Grandmother, take it easy.

17:28.800 --> 17:29.481
Let's leave.

17:33.041 --> 17:35.441
Mother, you and Father
were always at odds.

17:35.511 --> 17:36.800
You've been lonely and resentful,

17:37.341 --> 17:39.080
and that's why you raised
Dou Zhao this way

17:39.281 --> 17:40.400
to spite the Dou family?

17:46.921 --> 17:48.160
The fire is already lit.

17:48.880 --> 17:50.400
All that's left is to pour oil.

17:55.080 --> 17:56.041
What did you say?

17:56.600 --> 17:58.001
Shishu, stop it.

17:58.001 --> 17:58.600
Mother.

17:59.320 --> 17:59.961
Mother,

18:00.320 --> 18:01.600
please don't misunderstand.

18:01.961 --> 18:04.360
Shiying has the family's
best interests at heart.

18:04.361 --> 18:06.681
When you provided grain
to support disaster relief efforts,

18:06.921 --> 18:08.521
Shiying went to the court specifically

18:08.521 --> 18:09.891
to request a commendation for you.

18:10.120 --> 18:12.560
He planned to present it
at the family banquet

18:12.560 --> 18:13.721
to honor you.

18:17.741 --> 18:22.101
(Commendation)

18:24.961 --> 18:26.281
You sought a commendation

18:27.640 --> 18:29.041
just to persuade me

18:29.281 --> 18:31.120
to agree to Dou Zhao's marriage?

18:33.001 --> 18:34.241
I thought

18:35.441 --> 18:37.481
you cared about me.

18:38.360 --> 18:39.041
Mother,

18:39.640 --> 18:41.120
I genuinely care about you.

18:41.481 --> 18:43.281
I have no intent to deceive or barter.

18:43.521 --> 18:44.201
That's right,

18:44.360 --> 18:46.831
Shiying genuinely wants
to bring you and Zhao back to the manor

18:47.001 --> 18:48.360
so that you may live in happiness.

18:49.141 --> 18:51.031
Do you think that Dou Zhao
will be at your mercy

18:51.120 --> 18:52.840
once she's at the manor?

18:54.241 --> 18:55.441
Let me tell you,

18:55.840 --> 18:57.640
as long as I still draw breath,

18:58.160 --> 19:00.160
Dou Zhao will stay here with me.

19:00.321 --> 19:02.080
If the Wei family wants
to propose marriage,

19:02.400 --> 19:04.880
they'll have to get through
our gates first.

19:07.120 --> 19:07.921
Mother.

19:09.961 --> 19:10.640
Mother.

19:12.191 --> 19:13.640
Mother, I didn't mean it like that.

19:14.521 --> 19:16.001
This is too much.

19:16.281 --> 19:17.880
Why should I be caught in the middle?

19:18.400 --> 19:19.001
Mother,

19:19.681 --> 19:21.320
Shiying and I didn't mean it like that.

19:21.481 --> 19:22.080
Mother,

19:22.201 --> 19:23.681
please don't take it to heart.

19:24.600 --> 19:26.761
Take it easy, Mother.

19:36.600 --> 19:37.831
Years ago, you killed my mother,

19:38.360 --> 19:39.201
took my home,

19:39.421 --> 19:40.400
and schemed against me.

19:40.400 --> 19:41.600
I didn't hold it against you.

19:42.721 --> 19:44.160
Since returning here,

19:44.771 --> 19:46.041
I haven't competed with you once.

19:47.080 --> 19:48.471
But as long as you remain unmarried,

19:48.481 --> 19:51.360
I can't have peace
as the mistress of the Dou family.

19:52.001 --> 19:53.921
My grandmother is the
dearest person to me.

19:54.761 --> 19:56.281
If you dare to scheme against her again

19:57.041 --> 19:58.041
and cause her pain,

19:59.080 --> 20:00.921
I'll make you suffer a hundredfold.

20:02.201 --> 20:02.921
Dou Zhao,

20:03.120 --> 20:03.761
come back.

20:04.521 --> 20:05.761
Don't waste words with her.

20:17.320 --> 20:18.080
Does it hurt?

20:20.560 --> 20:22.201
Not anymore.

20:23.600 --> 20:24.281
I'd forgotten

20:25.080 --> 20:26.281
to hit her back.

20:28.681 --> 20:30.281
They talk about ethics and morality,

20:30.640 --> 20:32.320
but their actions are disgraceful.

20:32.840 --> 20:35.521
As expected of the son
of that brute, Dou Duo.

20:37.721 --> 20:39.721
You never speak of Grandfather.

20:40.441 --> 20:42.360
What really happened back then?

20:44.521 --> 20:46.600
I won't let you follow in my footsteps.

20:47.721 --> 20:48.721
Dou Duo and I

20:49.761 --> 20:52.560
were victims of an arranged marriage.

20:55.681 --> 20:58.921
That marriage ruined my entire life.

21:00.481 --> 21:02.481
It also destroyed Ms. Tuo's life.

21:03.320 --> 21:04.080
Ms. Tuo?

21:06.360 --> 21:08.360
Wasn't she my mother's personal maid?

21:08.961 --> 21:10.241
Why was she involved?

21:10.840 --> 21:13.281
Ms. Tuo was originally a maid
from my maiden family.

21:14.481 --> 21:16.360
But Dou Duo was debauched and lustful.

21:16.861 --> 21:18.961
It was one thing for him
to indulge with concubines,

21:20.001 --> 21:22.600
but he even preyed on relatives
and servants.

21:24.041 --> 21:26.840
I can't count how many messes
I've cleaned up for him.

21:27.600 --> 21:28.600
But I never expected

21:30.001 --> 21:33.921
he'd lay hands on Ms. Tuo,
who was already betrothed.

21:34.600 --> 21:36.600
I struck Dou Duo with a bottle

21:37.120 --> 21:38.600
to save Ms. Tuo.

21:39.880 --> 21:41.080
In the Dou household,

21:41.721 --> 21:44.921
no one condemned Dou Duo's
depravity or violence.

21:45.160 --> 21:47.400
Instead, they accused me
of injuring my husband,

21:48.441 --> 21:49.840
a violation punishable by divorce.

21:51.600 --> 21:53.880
They didn't dare offend
the prominent Cui family,

21:54.521 --> 21:56.080
so they sent me to this manor

21:56.921 --> 21:58.400
and treated me like a cast-off wife.

22:05.281 --> 22:06.521
You hurt Father this badly

22:06.761 --> 22:08.041
and disgraced the family.

22:08.320 --> 22:09.360
I don't deserve

22:09.360 --> 22:11.800
a wicked mother like you.

22:12.241 --> 22:13.360
Leave now!

22:13.521 --> 22:14.160
Shut the door.

22:17.640 --> 22:19.241
I can ignore

22:19.241 --> 22:20.721
their words and actions.

22:21.600 --> 22:23.481
But my own son

22:23.840 --> 22:25.761
treating me like a poisonous snake,

22:27.241 --> 22:29.120
denouncing me as unworthy
of being a mother...

22:32.441 --> 22:35.120
No wonder you never use the Dou surname

22:35.761 --> 22:36.921
and avoid the Dou's Residence.

22:39.600 --> 22:41.481
Such a family is no family at all.

22:42.120 --> 22:43.621
They don't deserve to be called family.

22:44.560 --> 22:45.481
So, Grandmother,

22:46.201 --> 22:47.921
you shouldn't feel sad because of them.

22:48.600 --> 22:50.080
We don't need this family.

22:50.491 --> 22:51.681
As long as we have each other,

22:51.961 --> 22:53.761
Sister, Ansu, and the others,

22:54.281 --> 22:56.080
this manor is our true home.

22:58.001 --> 22:59.080
You sweet child,

22:59.761 --> 23:00.961
always trying to cheer me up.

23:30.481 --> 23:31.041
Look at me.

23:33.281 --> 23:34.521
You got it on my face.

23:42.560 --> 23:44.001
Apologies for my sudden visit.

23:45.451 --> 23:46.281
Pardon my rudeness.

23:47.360 --> 23:48.320
Not at all.

23:50.921 --> 23:51.681
Su, let's go.

23:51.961 --> 23:52.521
Come on.

23:55.120 --> 23:55.921
Cousin.

24:00.880 --> 24:02.721
Mr. Wu, will you stay for dinner?

24:02.761 --> 24:04.120
I'll prepare chicken stew for you.

24:04.120 --> 24:04.560
Let's go.

24:05.201 --> 24:06.001
Bye.

24:07.961 --> 24:10.840
I'll wait for you back at the manor.

24:11.721 --> 24:12.360
It's fine.

24:14.241 --> 24:16.400
You've come from afar,
you must have an urgent matter.

24:17.320 --> 24:18.400
You can tell me right now.

24:19.041 --> 24:20.001
I won't mind.

24:24.521 --> 24:25.120
You may leave.

24:26.160 --> 24:26.560
Yes.

24:36.160 --> 24:36.880
I thought

24:37.041 --> 24:39.531
you had followed the Seventh Master
and moved to the capital.

24:40.041 --> 24:42.581
When I reached the Dou's Residence,
you were nowhere to be found.

24:42.840 --> 24:43.320
I...

24:44.080 --> 24:44.961
I...

24:45.320 --> 24:46.880
was so anxious that I rushed here.

24:50.681 --> 24:52.921
In order to save me
at the Dragon Boat Festival,

24:54.521 --> 24:55.160
you...

24:57.400 --> 24:58.400
you removed my clothes.

24:59.360 --> 25:01.241
It was a matter of life and death.

25:02.360 --> 25:04.360
Even if it were an old farmer,

25:04.560 --> 25:05.681
I would have done the same.

25:06.640 --> 25:08.080
You needn't dwell on it.

25:09.120 --> 25:10.581
You are magnanimous and open-minded,

25:10.761 --> 25:11.681
but as a man,

25:11.961 --> 25:13.600
how can I let your reputation
be tainted?

25:14.080 --> 25:15.481
I should take responsibility.

25:18.521 --> 25:19.560
And I'm willing to do so.

25:20.351 --> 25:22.401
I will ask the Wei family
to annul their engagement,

25:22.481 --> 25:24.521
then proceed with the proper
betrothal rites,

25:25.080 --> 25:25.961
and formally marry you.

25:31.600 --> 25:32.360
Mr. Wu,

25:34.041 --> 25:36.080
you and I have only met
three times before.

25:37.041 --> 25:38.761
How can we base a lifetime commitment

25:39.241 --> 25:40.320
on just three meetings?

25:41.241 --> 25:42.281
You treat me sincerely,

25:42.840 --> 25:44.160
so I must speak honestly.

25:45.080 --> 25:46.201
I don't wish to marry you

25:46.880 --> 25:47.840
or Wei Tingyu.

25:52.320 --> 25:54.640
A bet's a bet, nine taels of silver.

25:55.201 --> 25:55.961
Hand it over.

25:58.041 --> 25:59.800
So he really came to propose.

26:00.281 --> 26:02.080
Why doesn't any young master

26:02.080 --> 26:03.821
ever insist on taking responsibility
for me?

26:04.081 --> 26:05.831
All right, I'll take responsibility
for you.

26:07.400 --> 26:08.041
Let's go.

26:11.041 --> 26:12.640
I am captivated by your character.

26:13.801 --> 26:14.921
I think of you day and night.

26:16.320 --> 26:17.120
I believe

26:19.001 --> 26:20.201
we are kindred spirits.

26:22.241 --> 26:25.201
However, our family backgrounds
are incompatible.

26:26.201 --> 26:27.441
I don't care about status.

26:27.851 --> 26:29.080
You may not care about status,

26:29.880 --> 26:31.600
but it does dictate one's life.

26:32.251 --> 26:33.491
The poet, Li Yishan once said,

26:34.320 --> 26:36.961
“Washing one's feet in a clear spring,
sipping tea before flowers,

26:37.640 --> 26:39.521
these are vulgar acts
that spoil the scenery.”

26:40.360 --> 26:41.521
Yet I do so every day,

26:42.360 --> 26:43.600
and find it carefree and joyful.

26:44.481 --> 26:45.360
But this kind of joy

26:46.281 --> 26:48.320
is not permitted by noble families.

26:50.120 --> 26:51.800
I understand, I truly do.

27:05.640 --> 27:06.481
What you can't have,

27:07.880 --> 27:09.080
you yearn even more.

27:12.761 --> 27:14.481
The fame and pride of noble families

27:15.400 --> 27:17.681
is a cage to me.

27:18.800 --> 27:21.681
Love, marriage and reputation,

27:22.360 --> 27:23.241
all are burdens.

27:24.241 --> 27:25.600
I don't wish to be a virtuous wife.

27:27.001 --> 27:30.080
I only wish for a small boat
in the spring breeze,

27:30.560 --> 27:31.400
flowers by the shore,

27:32.481 --> 27:33.400
and wine in my cup.

27:35.201 --> 27:35.840
I understand.

27:37.961 --> 27:39.441
Because I admire your character,

27:39.840 --> 27:42.761
I will do my utmost to protect you
from those constraints.

27:43.640 --> 27:44.761
Mr. Wu,

27:46.120 --> 27:47.171
I appreciate your kindness.

27:48.001 --> 27:49.241
But did your grandfather

27:49.241 --> 27:51.320
consult you when he appointed you

27:52.160 --> 27:53.481
to the Ministry of Rites?

27:58.241 --> 28:00.041
Even you are not free
to act for yourself.

28:00.880 --> 28:02.640
Why think about protecting someone else?

28:05.160 --> 28:07.241
I wish you good health

28:07.600 --> 28:08.600
and a flourishing career.

28:09.521 --> 28:11.041
We shan't meet again.

28:17.451 --> 28:18.241
Fourth Young Lady...

28:27.080 --> 28:29.721
I made this myself.

28:30.501 --> 28:31.881
It's not only a token of gratitude,

28:33.481 --> 28:34.320
but also a couplet.

28:35.640 --> 28:36.761
Please accept it.

28:41.800 --> 28:43.600
"Divided by words of a kindred spirit,"

28:44.001 --> 28:46.120
"seeking a bond to soar as one."

28:46.681 --> 28:49.600
"A sincere heart dares to be
tested by simplicity."

28:52.640 --> 28:54.120
I'm no good at poetry,

28:54.481 --> 28:57.041
but I know the words "heart" and "dare"
make "simplicity".

29:01.041 --> 29:02.141
It's a brilliant couplet,

29:02.841 --> 29:05.031
but unfortunately, it's directed
at the wrong person.

29:05.921 --> 29:06.600
Dou Zhao,

29:07.320 --> 29:09.281
weren't you even a little moved?

29:10.521 --> 29:12.441
Love is a two-way street.

29:12.800 --> 29:14.721
Stop saying things that will upset Zhao.

29:16.921 --> 29:19.560
"A woman's infatuation
cannot be spoken of."

29:20.800 --> 29:21.840
The price of being moved

29:23.600 --> 29:24.441
is too high.

29:24.961 --> 29:27.201
I noticed his hands were calloused.

29:27.481 --> 29:28.880
He must be skilled in woodworking.

29:29.400 --> 29:31.160
Yet he never mentioned it

29:31.160 --> 29:32.560
in front of others.

29:33.320 --> 29:35.400
Craftsmanship is considered lowly work.

29:36.041 --> 29:37.080
Even if he enjoys it,

29:38.080 --> 29:39.600
he has to hide it away.

29:41.080 --> 29:43.640
Ladies, the Fifth Young Lady
sent handmade dumplings

29:43.640 --> 29:45.360
from the capital.

29:50.201 --> 29:51.281
There's meat dumpling,

29:52.241 --> 29:53.400
sesame dumpling,

29:54.080 --> 29:55.171
and red bean paste dumpling.

29:55.521 --> 29:56.481
Very thoughtful of her.

29:59.681 --> 30:02.080
(The night before the fifteenth,
the moonlight is clear.)

30:02.481 --> 30:03.880
(I miss you and Grandmother dearly,)

30:04.320 --> 30:05.721
(so I made these dumplings for you.)

30:06.001 --> 30:07.281
(I hope they bring joy.)

30:08.241 --> 30:10.120
(Though tonight isn't
the Lantern Festival,)

30:10.351 --> 30:12.080
(I wish the family
is together and whole,)

30:12.241 --> 30:13.320
(like the moon above.)

30:14.201 --> 30:16.961
(I hope we can be reunited soon.)

30:18.201 --> 30:19.281
(Regards, Ming.)

30:20.251 --> 30:22.431
Wang Yingxue doesn't want you
to return to the capital,

30:22.441 --> 30:24.471
but she doesn't seem to share
her mother's feelings

30:24.481 --> 30:25.560
and hopes for your return.

30:25.840 --> 30:27.441
Who knows if it's sincere or not?

30:29.921 --> 30:31.041
(After all that's happened,)

30:31.800 --> 30:34.441
(refusing marriage to Wei Tingyu,
meeting Wu Shan,)

30:35.160 --> 30:36.831
(and Wang Yingxue's
increasing hostility,)

30:37.721 --> 30:40.921
(Dou Ming doesn't seem as hypocritical
as I imagined.)

30:43.080 --> 30:44.211
Whether it's sincere or not,

30:44.441 --> 30:46.481
your true home is here.

30:46.600 --> 30:48.080
We are your family,

30:48.080 --> 30:48.800
right?

30:49.360 --> 30:49.921
Right.

30:54.901 --> 30:56.631
The Marquis of Jining sent gifts in return.

30:56.641 --> 30:59.231
He sent many brushes and ink
to Seventh Master and Fifth Master.

30:59.241 --> 31:02.481
Knowing Fifth Young Lady loves calligraphy
and painting, he sent her premium paper.

31:02.961 --> 31:06.160
This paper is sturdier
than what we usually use.

31:07.360 --> 31:08.721
It's not made from sandalwood bark.

31:13.600 --> 31:14.840
It's made from mulberry bark.

31:15.561 --> 31:17.360
The branches of this tree,
if left to grow,

31:17.551 --> 31:19.120
could shelter people from wind and rain.

31:19.441 --> 31:22.120
Its fruits can fill stomachs
and relieve hunger.

31:23.201 --> 31:25.761
Mulberry bark can also
be made into paper.

31:26.800 --> 31:28.800
The two simply have different purposes.

31:29.360 --> 31:30.600
Why rank one over the other?

31:31.681 --> 31:32.961
People are the same.

31:33.681 --> 31:35.320
What about mulberry bark?

31:38.721 --> 31:39.560
Nothing.

31:40.840 --> 31:41.880
Father loves making books.

31:42.360 --> 31:43.521
He uses a lot of paper.

31:43.880 --> 31:45.241
Send it to Father's study.

31:46.400 --> 31:46.961
Yes.

31:56.681 --> 31:57.491
Hurry up.

31:57.491 --> 31:58.360
All right, all right.

31:58.360 --> 32:00.001
Remember

32:00.001 --> 32:01.241
what I just said.

32:01.360 --> 32:02.201
Yes, yes.

32:02.201 --> 32:02.761
Official Wu.

32:03.160 --> 32:03.721
Official Wu.

32:04.001 --> 32:05.001
Official Dou.

32:06.281 --> 32:09.001
Recently, the Censorate
and the Six Ministries

32:09.281 --> 32:10.961
rejected my memorials.

32:11.201 --> 32:13.961
I had no choice but to bring them here.

32:15.360 --> 32:18.201
The Grand Secretariat
still upholds its integrity.

32:20.120 --> 32:23.281
Official Dou, you needn't
trouble yourself.

32:44.961 --> 32:47.441
For the sake of Yingxue and Shiying,

32:48.001 --> 32:49.400
I'll leave you with some advice.

32:50.640 --> 32:53.281
"The world is filled with perils
caused by human desires."

32:54.041 --> 32:56.021
"How many have been misled
and lost everything?"

33:32.961 --> 33:33.560
Mother.

33:35.800 --> 33:36.400
Yantang.

33:37.721 --> 33:39.120
Uncle's ship has docked today.

33:39.121 --> 33:40.851
I'm heading there with Gu Yu
to meet him.

33:43.640 --> 33:45.241
Since you're receiving your uncle,

33:46.360 --> 33:48.880
remember, the Jiang family's reputation
cannot be lost.

33:49.441 --> 33:50.160
Rest assured,

33:50.281 --> 33:52.041
I've made all the arrangements
in the court.

33:52.360 --> 33:53.400
Uncle will be fine.

33:54.241 --> 33:57.041
Perhaps he'll meet the Emperor
during the day,

33:57.560 --> 33:58.961
and by night, we'll reunite.

33:59.481 --> 34:00.560
The impeachment memorials

34:01.521 --> 34:03.481
have been submitted.

34:04.481 --> 34:06.880
This is the perfect time
for the Emperor and your uncle

34:07.041 --> 34:08.600
to have a proper conversation.

34:09.361 --> 34:10.361
It's a good thing.

34:13.091 --> 34:14.931
Given the Dou family's
questionable behavior,

34:14.961 --> 34:16.851
you still trust
the Fourth Young Lady's words?

34:17.511 --> 34:19.640
You might as well hand yourself
over to the Emperor.

34:20.080 --> 34:21.280
We're all players in this game.

34:22.280 --> 34:23.921
Even if she sees me as a chess piece,

34:24.181 --> 34:26.031
who's to say I'm not the one
moving the pieces?

34:26.441 --> 34:28.731
When I meet the Emperor,
I'll explain everything myself.

34:28.741 --> 34:30.581
Traveling by water must
take a toll on Uncle.

34:30.600 --> 34:31.811
Prepare to change his dressing.

34:36.080 --> 34:36.441
Gu Yu,

34:36.961 --> 34:38.200
isn't that Uncle's sedan chair?

34:43.401 --> 34:43.841
Stop!

34:50.401 --> 34:51.080
It's empty.

34:53.221 --> 34:53.741
Where is he?

35:04.881 --> 35:05.640
Move aside!

35:08.280 --> 35:08.841
Move aside!

35:11.680 --> 35:12.841
Sir, you cannot enter.

35:12.841 --> 35:13.680
You dare stop me?

35:14.001 --> 35:14.560
Move aside!

35:17.321 --> 35:18.080
Get out of the way!

35:18.080 --> 35:20.120
- Sir, you cannot enter.
- You mustn't enter, Sir!

35:20.120 --> 35:20.640
Stop this!

35:20.640 --> 35:21.361
Earl Yunyang.

35:21.371 --> 35:22.760
(Wang Yuan, Chief Eunuch)
Earl Yunyang.

35:22.760 --> 35:23.481
Earl Yunyang.

35:23.481 --> 35:24.411
We are handling a case.

35:24.421 --> 35:25.691
Do not obstruct official duties.

35:25.691 --> 35:26.560
Magistrate Dai.

35:27.441 --> 35:28.280
Eunuch Wang.

35:28.640 --> 35:29.961
What are you both doing here?

35:30.301 --> 35:31.200
Fulfilling our duties.

35:31.521 --> 35:32.361
Yes.

35:33.240 --> 35:34.680
Who's up there? I'll go see.

35:35.401 --> 35:36.041
Earl Yunyang,

35:36.680 --> 35:37.760
you mustn't go up.

35:37.881 --> 35:39.080
But I insist.

35:39.481 --> 35:39.961
Please...

35:39.961 --> 35:40.680
- Move aside.
- Earl Yunyang.

35:40.680 --> 35:41.760
- Don't.
- Move aside.

35:41.760 --> 35:42.361
Earl Yunyang!

36:46.441 --> 36:47.001
Uncle.

36:47.361 --> 36:48.280
Wake up.

36:50.921 --> 36:51.521
Uncle...

36:52.280 --> 36:53.720
Wake up.

36:54.401 --> 36:55.680
Uncle!

37:02.801 --> 37:04.961
Why?

37:07.240 --> 37:07.760
How dare you!

37:07.761 --> 37:08.851
How dare you disrupt a case.

37:08.861 --> 37:09.921
Do you have a death wish?

37:12.321 --> 37:13.361
Get out!

37:13.801 --> 37:14.481
General.

37:16.041 --> 37:16.680
General.

37:17.781 --> 37:19.760
The Shadow Guard operates
under imperial orders.

37:20.080 --> 37:22.001
Anyone interfering is guilty of treason.

37:22.701 --> 37:24.841
General, please disembark the boat
with Earl Yunyang.

37:25.261 --> 37:27.120
Was the Emperor's order
to bring Duke of Ding

37:27.120 --> 37:28.600
safely to the capital,

37:28.801 --> 37:30.361
or to return with his corpse?

37:31.240 --> 37:31.961
General,

37:32.441 --> 37:34.720
you mustn't speculate
about the Emperor's intentions.

37:35.160 --> 37:37.600
Duke of Ding was assassinated
last night by sea bandits.

37:38.051 --> 37:39.831
The Shadow Guards responsible
for his escort

37:39.841 --> 37:42.001
failed in their duty
and perished as well.

37:43.640 --> 37:45.801
The sea bandits of Dongyu
always slash upwards.

37:46.521 --> 37:48.921
The wound should be wider at the top,

37:49.240 --> 37:50.801
but this is the opposite.

37:51.720 --> 37:52.401
Eunuch Wang,

37:53.001 --> 37:54.481
you must know this.

37:58.280 --> 37:59.441
Bandits are cunning.

37:59.961 --> 38:03.760
Perhaps this was
deliberate misdirection.

38:03.760 --> 38:04.600
Eunuch Wang,

38:04.921 --> 38:06.120
Duke of Ding is dead.

38:06.401 --> 38:07.200
Speak the truth.

38:08.641 --> 38:11.581
Duke of Ding's death is not the work
of the Northern Pacification Bureau,

38:11.881 --> 38:13.431
nor was it ordered by the Emperor.

38:13.451 --> 38:16.321
The incident happened suddenly, and we have
yet to report to the Emperor.

38:16.321 --> 38:18.131
General, please go back
and await the decree.

38:18.131 --> 38:20.521
The Ministry of Imperial Ceremony
will investigate thoroughly

38:20.521 --> 38:21.681
and give you an explanation.

38:43.001 --> 38:43.600
Uncle...

38:45.241 --> 38:47.120
If only I had returned
to the capital with you,

38:50.001 --> 38:51.640
this wouldn't have happened.

38:53.361 --> 38:55.240
We wouldn't have this outcome.

39:38.640 --> 39:39.801
You want me to wait?

39:39.801 --> 39:40.321
General!

39:40.371 --> 39:42.671
To wait while you fabricate
false charges against my uncle

39:42.681 --> 39:44.891
or issue an imperial decree
to exterminate our family?

39:44.901 --> 39:46.921
General, let's not be rash.

39:46.921 --> 39:47.760
Get out!

39:47.801 --> 39:49.200
Yantang, what are you doing?

39:49.301 --> 39:50.600
Since the Emperor doesn't know,

39:50.691 --> 39:52.760
I will take Eunuch Wang
to report directly to him.

39:52.801 --> 39:53.760
Yantang, calm down.

39:53.760 --> 39:55.441
General.

39:55.481 --> 39:56.080
Let me through!

39:56.600 --> 39:57.321
General...

40:10.061 --> 40:14.501
(The Grand Hall)

40:17.501 --> 40:19.621
(Lady Wan, the Empress)

40:20.001 --> 40:21.600
Straighten attire.

40:23.280 --> 40:24.401
Prepare to receive the gods.

40:25.240 --> 40:26.240
Maintain solemnity.

40:26.921 --> 40:28.001
Compose yourself.

40:28.680 --> 40:29.441
Kneel.

40:30.680 --> 40:31.481
Bow.

40:34.041 --> 40:35.640
Natural disasters plague the land.

40:36.441 --> 40:37.801
The common people are suffering.

40:38.720 --> 40:40.200
This is my fault.

40:41.240 --> 40:43.680
I humbly ask for divine protection.

40:44.481 --> 40:46.001
Bless my people.

40:46.801 --> 40:48.600
Let evil be eradicated.

40:49.600 --> 40:51.921
Grant peace and prosperity to the land.

40:54.200 --> 40:56.441
Yantang, that is a capital offense,

40:56.531 --> 40:57.441
please think carefully.

40:57.481 --> 40:59.441
If my life can preserve my uncle's honor

40:59.441 --> 41:00.801
and the lives of the Jiang family,

41:00.841 --> 41:01.560
it'll be worth it.

41:07.120 --> 41:08.600
Stand back! Don't come closer!

41:08.600 --> 41:09.481
I must see the Emperor!

41:12.921 --> 41:13.401
Stand back.

41:13.401 --> 41:13.961
Song Mo?

41:13.961 --> 41:14.881
We're on the same side!

41:15.200 --> 41:15.801
The same side!

41:16.280 --> 41:16.961
Gu Yu,

41:17.251 --> 41:20.120
breaking into the palace is a capital offense,
why didn't you stop him?

41:20.801 --> 41:21.401
Aunt,

41:21.401 --> 41:22.280
this is urgent.

41:22.441 --> 41:23.001
Move aside.

41:33.291 --> 41:35.241
A ruler may kill his minister
if he doubts him.

41:35.611 --> 41:37.280
If Your Majesty wanted Duke of Ding dead,

41:37.721 --> 41:39.280
a cup of poisoned wine would suffice.

41:40.200 --> 41:42.280
A man should maintain his dignity
even in death.

41:42.760 --> 41:44.801
Why the torture and humiliation?

41:45.680 --> 41:46.481
He's already dead.

41:47.441 --> 41:50.801
Why add insult to injury
by claiming he was killed

41:50.801 --> 41:53.001
by the very bandits he dedicated
his life to fighting?

41:54.120 --> 41:55.160
I, Song Mo,

41:55.720 --> 41:58.760
demand an answer,
so that I may die without regrets.

42:02.080 --> 42:03.271
No matter how great the issue,

42:03.381 --> 42:05.080
it does not justify
such insubordination.

42:07.560 --> 42:09.240
Who? Who has died?

42:09.801 --> 42:10.640
Your Majesty,

42:11.280 --> 42:12.401
Duke of Ding, Jiang Meisun,

42:12.641 --> 42:14.280
died in the ship's cabin
on his way back.

42:17.760 --> 42:18.680
How is this possible?

42:20.080 --> 42:22.560
I was waiting for him,

42:23.481 --> 42:25.001
waiting to question him.

42:27.560 --> 42:28.240
Who?

42:30.240 --> 42:31.921
Who dared to kill him?

42:32.280 --> 42:33.240
Who?

42:33.720 --> 42:34.401
Your Majesty.

42:38.961 --> 42:40.200
This is my uncle's keepsake,

42:41.280 --> 42:42.921
something he shared
with you in the past.

42:43.971 --> 42:45.031
Even in his final moments,

42:46.921 --> 42:48.401
he held onto it tightly.

42:49.841 --> 42:51.361
If there is a conspiracy,

42:52.160 --> 42:53.720
I beg Your Majesty to investigate.

43:13.080 --> 43:14.160
We were allies,

43:14.240 --> 43:16.640
but General Yan's threats to me

43:16.640 --> 43:18.041
indicate a different story.

43:18.560 --> 43:19.760
Your Majesty!

43:20.001 --> 43:21.521
Arrest this treasonous wretch.

43:21.521 --> 43:22.680
Take him away.

43:22.720 --> 43:25.841
What the General has done
is a capital offense.

43:25.841 --> 43:29.200
If you do not eliminate the problem
at its root, it will lead to disaster.

43:32.541 --> 43:35.861
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

43:36.381 --> 43:39.701
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

43:40.001 --> 43:45.441
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

43:46.351 --> 43:47.641
♪Where can this restless heart
find peace?♪

43:47.641 --> 43:50.581
♪Left alone in an empty hall♪

43:50.781 --> 43:54.301
♪A lifetime chasing fate's lonely call♪

43:54.661 --> 43:58.941
♪Watching seasons fade and storms rise♪

43:58.941 --> 44:01.521
♪It hurts but it's not all for nothing♪

44:01.521 --> 44:02.791
♪My heart is as empty as a quiet street♪

44:02.791 --> 44:05.551
♪Who cares about the path I walk alone?♪

44:05.761 --> 44:09.701
♪Would you take away
the weight of the past?♪

44:09.981 --> 44:11.911
♪Life is fleeting, like morning frost♪

44:11.911 --> 44:15.141
♪Even a moment feels endless with you♪

44:15.141 --> 44:21.161
♪Like a stream flowing steady
through time♪

44:23.241 --> 44:29.851
♪A lone flower falls from the eaves
Moonlight graces steps beneath♪

44:30.611 --> 44:37.601
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

44:38.171 --> 44:41.121
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

44:41.901 --> 44:45.311
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

44:45.631 --> 44:51.191
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

44:52.081 --> 44:53.361
♪In this chaotic world♪

44:53.361 --> 44:56.161
♪Only love lasts♪

44:56.301 --> 44:59.861
♪We'll get through
every challenge together♪

45:00.331 --> 45:04.561
♪No matter how cold
or uncertain the road♪

45:04.561 --> 45:07.141
♪There's nothing to fear
when I'm with you♪

45:07.141 --> 45:08.351
♪My heart feels empty♪

45:08.351 --> 45:11.191
♪But I can hear your voice♪

45:11.321 --> 45:15.381
♪In this life, under moonlight
and across the oceans♪

45:15.541 --> 45:17.711
♪We'll find our way back to each other♪

45:18.041 --> 45:18.881
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:18.891 --> 45:19.781
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:19.791 --> 45:20.771
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)

45:20.781 --> 45:26.031
♪Together, we'll make every moment count♪
